import React from 'react';
import { Form, Button, Col, Row } from 'react-bootstrap';

const ProfileForm = () => {
  return (
    <Form>
      <Form.Group controlId='formGridEmail'>
        <Form.Label>Company</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control placeholder="Enter your Company's Name" />
      </Form.Group>

      <Form.Group controlId='formGridPassword'>
        <Form.Label>Website</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control placeholder="Enter your website's Adress" />
      </Form.Group>

      <Form.Group controlId='formGridAddress1'>
        <Form.Label>Location</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control placeholder='1234 Main St' />
      </Form.Group>

      <Form.Group controlId='formGridAddress2'>
        <Form.Label>Skills</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control placeholder='Enter your skills' />
      </Form.Group>

      <Form.Row>
        <Form.Group as={Col} controlId='formGridCity'>
          <Form.Label>GitHub Username</Form.Label>
          <Form.Control placeholder="Enter your GitHub's Username" />
        </Form.Group>

        <Form.Group as={Col} controlId='formGridState'>
          <Form.Label>Bio</Form.Label>
          <Form.Control placeholder='Enter your Bio' />
        </Form.Group>

        <Form.Group as={Col} controlId='formGridState'>
          <Form.Label>LinkedIn</Form.Label>
          <Form.Control placeholder="Enter your LinkedIn's Username" />
        </Form.Group>

        <Form.Group as={Col} controlId='formGridZip'>
          <Form.Label>Youtube</Form.Label>
          <Form.Control placeholder="Enter your Youtube's Username" />
        </Form.Group>
      </Form.Row>

      <Form.Group id='formGridCheckbox'>
        <Form.Check type='checkbox' label='Check me out' />
      </Form.Group>

      <Button variant='primary' type='submit'>
        Submit
      </Button>
    </Form>
  );
};

export default ProfileForm;
